Moved with care it hardly made a noise.<br>
The figure who climbed out of the work access was bundled in an impossibly long full trench coat with a high collar turned up. Despite being covered from head to toe, the figure was obviously female. She teetered for a moment, balanced on the edge of the hole in ridiculous stilletto heels, while jamming her hat down with exagerated delicacy. After a careful dusting and adjusting, she curtsied and tittered towards a security camera she knew was perched under the eves of a nearby building.<br>
Blue green eyes sparkled with impish glee above a ratty but once expensive scarf wrapped securely around her face. She crouched by the access and reaching down hauled up a duffle bag nearly as big as herself. Bag secured, she replaced the manhole cover. Hoisting the bag over one shoulder she tottered down the side walk. She swayed and listed, but never lost her way.<br>
Behind her trailed a childish nonsense song, &quot;lollee lollee lee loo lee loo leeee&quot;, in a soft lisping voice, and a scent like flowers, like the memory of Mama's perfume, apple blossoms in the spring, fresh plums splitting in the summer heat, a drift of sweetness from a bakery's midnite baking, lingering hauntingly in her wake.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=90.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showNextMessage?topicID=90.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=90.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.threadControl?topicID=90.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=90.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=90.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="scbnforum58570frm12">Blackjack's Message Board <option value="scbnforum58570frm21">The Barrens<option value="scbnforum58570frm23">Domain Status<option value="scbnfo